Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万万不可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予破坏了仪式的污秽之徒们以星之审判
