Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢
